## Context

llama.cpp's `common/chat.cpp` contains a dispatch system for specialized chat template
handlers that format prompts for particular model families. Models like Mistral-7B-Instruct-v0.3
use a simple `[INST]`/`[/INST]` wrapping format (without `[SYSTEM_PROMPT]`). Currently no
